      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute beauty in person. It\u2019s a total gem and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one\u2014not a single scratch or dent to be found, and the interior still has that fresh scent. It drives like a dream and has been my absolute pride and joy. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new and has been loved every mile of the way, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 46500.0,
