    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a showroom-quality masterpiece. Meticulously maintained and collector-owned, the exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish completely free of stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks, further protected by a high-end ceramic coating. The interior is equally pristine, featuring supple leather seats with no visible wear, original factory floor mats, and that unmistakable new-car aroma. Every button, switch, and electronic component functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been serviced exclusively at certified dealerships with a full binder of records included. Always stored in a climate-controlled garage and never exposed to the elements, this vehicle drives with the tightness and precision of a brand-new car. It is, quite simply, the finest example currently on the market.",
      "price": 48500.0,
